WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:50.080 --> 01:51.840
- To compromise
- To compromise

01:51.920 --> 01:53.360
It's almost my dorm's curfew.

01:53.440 --> 01:54.680
Good!

01:56.000 --> 01:57.840
- I'll get going first.
- Next song.

01:57.920 --> 01:59.440
- Goodbye.
- Next song.

01:59.520 --> 02:00.720
- Pick a song.
- Pass me the mic.

02:00.800 --> 02:02.400
Pass the mic, Mingming. This is mine.

02:06.280 --> 02:07.560
Jiang Ying?

02:08.560 --> 02:10.039
How did you know I was here?

02:10.600 --> 02:11.680
Wait.

02:11.760 --> 02:13.920
Do you know that his dad is in a coma?

02:17.160 --> 02:18.760
I just don't want a young girl like you

02:18.840 --> 02:20.200
to be led astray.

02:21.760 --> 02:23.040
His dad's hospital bill

02:23.120 --> 02:25.560
costs nearly 100,000 yuan per year.

02:25.640 --> 02:27.440
No girl has the time and money

02:27.520 --> 02:28.560
to waste on him.

02:28.640 --> 02:29.840
I do.

02:32.360 --> 02:33.520
I can waste it on him.

02:35.840 --> 02:36.960
Then do you know

02:37.560 --> 02:39.240
that his dad killed someone while driving?

02:39.960 --> 02:41.200
He's a murderer.

02:42.200 --> 02:44.120
So what does that have to do
with Duan Jiaxu?

02:45.560 --> 02:46.400
Fine.

02:47.400 --> 02:48.280
You may not mind it.

02:48.960 --> 02:50.280
But your parents will never agree

02:50.360 --> 02:51.280
to your relationship.

02:56.920 --> 02:58.240
Don't bother worrying about me.

02:58.880 --> 03:00.480
Do you really think he likes you?

03:01.160 --> 03:02.880
Duan Jiaxu grew up without love

03:02.960 --> 03:04.360
due to family reasons.

03:05.040 --> 03:06.920
If anyone treats him well,

03:07.760 --> 03:09.480
he will think it is love.

03:10.240 --> 03:11.720
Do you treat him very nicely?

03:13.360 --> 03:14.880
If you think he likes you,

03:15.720 --> 03:17.560
then tell me what he likes about you.

03:19.920 --> 03:21.760
You've fallen head over heels for him.

03:22.240 --> 03:24.120
But what if you want to break up with him?

03:25.200 --> 03:26.320
Guess what he will say.

03:27.920 --> 03:29.720
Do you think he is pretty sensible?

03:32.000 --> 03:34.760
In reality, he won't even care.

03:34.840 --> 03:36.280
He couldn't care less

03:36.840 --> 03:37.880
about breaking up with you.

03:38.400 --> 03:39.360
He can find

03:40.240 --> 03:41.960
thousands of other girls like you.

03:44.040 --> 03:45.840
I hit the nail on the head, didn't I?

03:45.920 --> 03:47.800
- Let go.
- Why do you think I pick on him?

03:47.880 --> 03:49.360
- Why am I like this?
- Let go.

03:49.440 --> 03:51.080
His dad killed my dad!

03:55.880 --> 03:58.640
If your family experienced
something like this,

03:59.960 --> 04:01.760
wouldn't you become like me?

04:07.600 --> 04:08.480
I understand.

04:10.840 --> 04:12.160
But it was his dad

04:12.680 --> 04:13.960
who made the mistake.

04:14.640 --> 04:15.840
His dad committed the crime.

04:17.120 --> 04:18.480
He will bear legal responsibility.

04:19.360 --> 04:21.160
- He will--
- Receive his just punishment?

04:28.760 --> 04:32.080
Do you know that his dad
was a hit-and-runner?

04:32.640 --> 04:33.800
He was afraid of imprisonment.

04:34.760 --> 04:36.760
He was afraid of criticism.

04:36.840 --> 04:38.480
He attempted suicide. But in the end?

04:39.840 --> 04:40.840
His dad didn't die.

04:40.920 --> 04:42.400
My dad died instead.

04:43.000 --> 04:45.080
I was the one who was punished!

04:46.960 --> 04:48.360
So do you think Duan Jiaxu

04:48.440 --> 04:50.680
has nothing to do with this incident?

04:52.840 --> 04:53.760
Jiang Ying.

04:56.960 --> 04:58.280
Hasn't Duan Jiaxu

05:00.720 --> 05:02.680
already made up for his dad's sin?

05:04.480 --> 05:06.000
I know you're innocent.

05:06.080 --> 05:07.160
But

05:08.520 --> 05:09.720
isn't he innocent too?

05:11.600 --> 05:13.920
What exactly has Duan Jiaxu done wrong?

05:17.440 --> 05:18.280
You see,

05:20.360 --> 05:22.120
this isn't an excuse for you to hurt him.

05:42.120 --> 05:44.480
His dad killed my dad!

05:45.560 --> 05:46.840
So do you think Duan Jiaxu

05:46.920 --> 05:49.400
has nothing to do with this incident?

05:49.960 --> 05:52.680
If your family experienced
something like this,

05:55.920 --> 05:57.680
wouldn't you become like me?

06:01.560 --> 06:02.680
Let me tell you a secret.

06:03.800 --> 06:04.680
I have

06:06.120 --> 06:08.040
plenty of debtors out there.

06:09.160 --> 06:10.240
Actually,

06:10.800 --> 06:11.800
these aren't my debts.

06:12.600 --> 06:14.040
You don't need to help me repay them.

06:17.520 --> 06:18.480
In the past,

06:19.840 --> 06:21.760
is this how she made Jiaxu

06:23.680 --> 06:25.320
live in guilt?

06:30.760 --> 06:32.280
Why are you drinking?

06:35.400 --> 06:36.240
What's wrong?

06:39.280 --> 06:40.200
Are you in a bad mood?

06:45.360 --> 06:46.240
So?

06:46.960 --> 06:48.320
Did the gathering go well?

06:48.960 --> 06:50.400
I bought dessert for you.

06:51.360 --> 06:52.200
It's bread.

06:54.160 --> 06:55.080
Do you want to try it?

06:55.960 --> 06:57.040
It's adorable.

07:00.440 --> 07:01.600
Did something happen?

07:01.680 --> 07:03.320
Why are you sitting
by the riverside alone?

07:03.920 --> 07:05.000
It's windy out here.

07:05.080 --> 07:06.440
You're even drinking beer.

07:10.760 --> 07:11.640
Try it.

07:18.360 --> 07:19.200
Is it tasty?

07:20.200 --> 07:21.280
The ear is delicious.

07:21.840 --> 07:23.320
Now try the nose.

07:32.360 --> 07:33.280
Here you go.

07:37.840 --> 07:38.920
What's the meaning of this?

07:39.960 --> 07:41.320
I only bought you bread

07:41.400 --> 07:42.640
and you gave me your bank card.

07:47.200 --> 07:49.080
There's 5,000 yuan on the card.

07:50.440 --> 07:52.360
If I successfully complete my internship,

07:52.440 --> 07:53.560
I'll get another 3,000 yuan.

07:55.040 --> 07:56.080
In that case,

07:57.480 --> 07:58.760
there will be 8,000 yuan.

08:01.880 --> 08:03.520
Why are you suddenly giving me this?

08:05.560 --> 08:07.400
I just want to tell you

08:10.320 --> 08:11.640
that I can be nice to you.

08:12.960 --> 08:14.600
I can be nice to you for life.

08:16.800 --> 08:17.640
I'm serious.

08:30.120 --> 08:32.080
So our little Sang Zhi wants

08:32.159 --> 08:33.559
to take care of me.

08:38.200 --> 08:39.520
Take this.

08:40.120 --> 08:41.039
What?

08:41.120 --> 08:42.880
The PIN on my card is your birth date.

08:43.480 --> 08:44.880
You can use the money

08:44.960 --> 08:46.440
to buy beautiful dresses for yourself.

08:47.840 --> 08:49.120
As for this card,

08:49.760 --> 08:51.000
it's mine now.

08:53.560 --> 08:55.080
You have quite a lot of money.

08:56.480 --> 08:57.400
So…

08:58.160 --> 08:59.000
Boss.

08:59.680 --> 09:01.080
What are your orders?

09:03.520 --> 09:05.080
I can satisfy all of your desires.

09:10.800 --> 09:11.720
What?

09:11.800 --> 09:13.200
I know I'm corny.

09:14.840 --> 09:16.640
Do you finally admit it?

09:16.720 --> 09:18.640
I'm just joking. Am I really corny?

09:18.720 --> 09:19.560
Yes, you are.

09:24.200 --> 09:25.200
Take it back.

09:27.600 --> 09:29.040
There's no use giving this back.

09:29.120 --> 09:30.680
I won't return your card to you.

09:30.760 --> 09:32.040
I didn't ask you to.

09:34.520 --> 09:35.680
This is truly unexpected.

09:36.560 --> 09:37.560
At my age,

09:37.640 --> 09:39.320
there is still someone I can depend on.

09:39.400 --> 09:40.280
However,

09:41.720 --> 09:43.400
you can't spend recklessly.

09:43.480 --> 09:45.200
It's mine to do with now.

09:45.280 --> 09:46.920
Don't misspend. You need to save up.

09:47.000 --> 09:48.520
For what? Your dowry?

09:48.600 --> 09:50.080
Save up to buy a house.

09:51.800 --> 09:53.640
I seriously looked into it.

09:53.720 --> 09:55.920
For an approximately 100-square-meter unit

09:56.000 --> 09:57.440
located in downtown Yihe,

09:58.120 --> 10:00.720
the down payment is around 500,000 yuan.

10:01.680 --> 10:03.480
But don't worry.

10:04.840 --> 10:05.760
It will be quick.

10:06.720 --> 10:08.120
We'll have enough money in 50 years.

10:13.640 --> 10:14.480
Sure.

10:15.760 --> 10:16.680
I'll wait

10:17.240 --> 10:18.960
for you to buy a huge house,

10:19.520 --> 10:20.800
so I can hide my mistress there.

10:21.720 --> 10:22.920
What a headache.

10:34.160 --> 10:35.000
Boss.

10:37.400 --> 10:38.240
Keep this.

10:40.280 --> 10:42.040
I told you I don't need it.

10:46.000 --> 10:47.160
I already told you.

10:47.880 --> 10:48.960
I'm depending on you now.

10:49.520 --> 10:50.520
With you around,

10:50.600 --> 10:52.400
I don't need to save money for myself.

10:53.400 --> 10:55.320
I spend lavishly.

10:55.400 --> 10:57.160
Can you spend as quickly as I earn it?

11:03.480 --> 11:05.520
I guess I'll keep it for you.

11:06.240 --> 11:07.440
However,

11:07.520 --> 11:08.960
if you need to use money,

11:09.040 --> 11:10.120
just tell me.

11:10.200 --> 11:11.600
I'll give it to you, okay?

11:12.200 --> 11:13.080
Okay.

11:29.640 --> 11:30.480
Sang Zhi.

11:32.240 --> 11:33.960
If you're upset about something,

11:34.560 --> 11:35.880
you can talk to me about it.

11:35.960 --> 11:36.840
I'm not upset.

11:38.400 --> 11:40.160
I'm already happy

11:40.240 --> 11:42.120
that you came to get me.

12:11.360 --> 12:13.560
CHAPTER 20, SAFEGUARD

12:13.640 --> 12:15.160
ONE PATH, TWO PEOPLE

12:17.920 --> 12:19.440
Sang Zhi, are you still working?

12:19.520 --> 12:21.360
It's time to eat. Continue after eating.

12:21.440 --> 12:23.200
It's fine. I'll be done soon.

12:23.280 --> 12:24.280
I'll go after this.

12:24.360 --> 12:25.280
You guys can go ahead.

12:25.360 --> 12:26.240
Okay.

12:26.320 --> 12:27.800
Let's go eat.

12:31.640 --> 12:34.280
Media analysis…

12:35.680 --> 12:37.280
Sang Zhi, this is your order.

12:37.360 --> 12:38.720
I brought it in on my way.

12:38.800 --> 12:40.080
I didn't order any food delivery.

12:40.160 --> 12:41.360
Isn't this your phone number?

12:41.960 --> 12:43.840
SOMEONE SENT THIS
TO TELL YOU THAT THEY MISS YOU

12:43.920 --> 12:46.120
PLEASE GIVE YOUR SWEETIE
A FIVE-STAR RATING AFTER RECEIPT!

12:47.360 --> 12:49.160
I see. Thank you.

12:49.880 --> 12:50.720
Thank you.

13:17.400 --> 13:19.920
If you ever need to work late again,

13:20.000 --> 13:21.200
just tell me.

13:21.280 --> 13:22.160
I'll pick you up.

13:23.240 --> 13:25.240
The campus is deserted during the summer.

13:25.320 --> 13:27.000
It's dangerous, all right?

13:27.080 --> 13:29.000
Working during the day is tiring enough.

13:29.080 --> 13:30.480
You even work overtime at night.

13:30.560 --> 13:31.800
If you pick me up,

13:31.880 --> 13:33.080
won't it be exhausting for you

13:33.160 --> 13:34.320
to travel back and forth?

13:35.360 --> 13:36.280
Yes.

13:36.840 --> 13:37.760
So what should we do?

13:39.640 --> 13:40.960
Why don't you move in with me?

13:47.560 --> 13:49.120
They check on me every night.

13:51.840 --> 13:52.840
Hello, Mom.

13:52.920 --> 13:53.760
Hello, Zhizhi.

13:54.560 --> 13:55.520
Where are you?

13:56.160 --> 13:57.160
Are you still working?

13:58.560 --> 13:59.640
I'll reach the dorm soon.

13:59.720 --> 14:00.640
I'm on my way back.

14:01.520 --> 14:02.800
Are you only heading home now?

14:03.400 --> 14:05.480
It's late. Is it safe to be alone outside?

14:05.560 --> 14:08.840
I do worry since you're there alone.

14:09.440 --> 14:10.640
It's fine.

14:10.720 --> 14:12.880
I'm not the only one doing an internship.

14:12.960 --> 14:14.880
Plenty of students here are interning.

14:14.960 --> 14:16.240
You don't need to worry about me.

14:16.320 --> 14:18.560
Give me a video call
after you reach the dorm.

14:19.840 --> 14:21.720
Be careful on the road. Bye.

14:21.800 --> 14:22.840
Bye.

14:24.840 --> 14:26.080
Did you see that?

14:26.160 --> 14:27.120
That's fine.

14:27.200 --> 14:28.720
I'll just put in a little extra effort

14:28.800 --> 14:30.320
and pick you up after work every day.

14:31.400 --> 14:32.680
Really?

14:32.760 --> 14:33.800
Just wait and see.

14:41.840 --> 14:42.760
Sang Yan?

14:45.240 --> 14:46.960
Why is he calling me after blocking me?

14:48.160 --> 14:49.800
What is it?

14:51.840 --> 14:53.040
Are you back at your dorm?

14:54.040 --> 14:55.480
I'm almost there.

14:55.560 --> 14:56.480
What's the matter?

14:58.280 --> 14:59.880
There's a girl holding hands

15:00.760 --> 15:02.800
with a guy on campus right now.

15:04.040 --> 15:04.920
That's you, right?

15:16.280 --> 15:18.920
Did you come to Yihe?

15:21.520 --> 15:22.760
Am I blind?

15:35.800 --> 15:37.640
Why does your postgraduate boyfriend

15:39.360 --> 15:42.120
look just like Duan Jiaxu?

15:54.440 --> 15:57.000
Why didn't you tell me
that you were coming?

15:57.640 --> 15:58.840
I could've picked you up.

16:08.760 --> 16:09.600
Well…

16:10.200 --> 16:11.880
He has a generic face.

16:12.960 --> 16:15.560
They just look alike.

16:16.280 --> 16:17.240
It's very common.

16:19.520 --> 16:20.360
Sang Zhi.

16:20.440 --> 16:22.560
Do you really take me for a fool?

16:23.920 --> 16:25.240
I'll help you come up with excuses

16:25.320 --> 16:26.800
for why you're holding his hand.

16:26.880 --> 16:29.760
Is Duan Jiaxu crippled, blind, or drunk?

16:29.840 --> 16:30.840
Make your choice.

16:30.920 --> 16:32.720
I guess he's drunk.

16:32.800 --> 16:33.880
Is that okay?

16:33.960 --> 16:35.400
So to support him,

16:35.480 --> 16:36.640
you have to hold his hand.

16:40.920 --> 16:42.120
Will you believe that?

16:43.680 --> 16:44.560
Come here.

16:46.440 --> 16:47.400
Come here.

16:54.040 --> 16:55.120
I don't think

16:55.920 --> 16:57.960
I have a generic face.

17:11.400 --> 17:12.680
I pursued her.

17:33.600 --> 17:34.480
It will be fine.

17:47.120 --> 17:49.120
Sang Yan, what's wrong with you?

17:49.960 --> 17:51.480
I didn't hide it from you.

17:51.560 --> 17:52.960
I wanted to tell you.

17:53.040 --> 17:56.200
I did tell you, but you blocked me.

17:56.280 --> 17:57.200
See for yourself.

17:58.960 --> 17:59.920
Postgraduate student?

18:02.600 --> 18:03.760
- Postgraduate student.
- Well…

18:05.040 --> 18:05.880
I'm sorry.

18:05.960 --> 18:08.000
I lied to you about that.

18:08.080 --> 18:09.840
But I just wanted you

18:09.920 --> 18:11.080
to be mentally prepared.

18:11.160 --> 18:13.520
Mentally prepared for our age gap,

18:13.600 --> 18:16.240
even though Jiaxu
isn't too much older than me.

18:16.320 --> 18:17.840
How far is your dorm?

18:19.320 --> 18:20.880
It's just up ahead.

18:25.560 --> 18:26.600
It will be fine.

18:26.680 --> 18:27.960
I'll talk to your brother later.

18:31.720 --> 18:33.840
Where will you be staying later?

18:33.920 --> 18:35.360
Let me get a place for you.

18:36.000 --> 18:36.960
Mind your own business.

18:38.440 --> 18:40.720
Don't be like this. Come on.

18:40.800 --> 18:42.160
If you like any one of my friends,

18:42.240 --> 18:43.320
I'll introduce them to you.

18:43.400 --> 18:45.440
- I wouldn't be angry like you.
- I don't need it.

18:45.520 --> 18:47.360
Everyone eventually gets married.

18:47.440 --> 18:48.560
Why don't you need it?

18:48.640 --> 18:50.400
Dating is a normal thing.

18:50.480 --> 18:51.840
Don't you want to date?

18:51.920 --> 18:52.800
Is it this building?

18:55.440 --> 18:56.920
It's right inside.

18:58.320 --> 18:59.240
Go in.

19:00.840 --> 19:01.760
Go now.

19:02.400 --> 19:03.840
You have to video call your mom.

19:07.560 --> 19:09.880
It's not like you don't know who Jiaxu is.

19:09.960 --> 19:11.280
You know his character.

19:11.360 --> 19:12.960
What do I know about his character?

19:13.040 --> 19:13.920
Please enlighten me.

19:14.920 --> 19:16.000
Don't be like this.

19:16.680 --> 19:17.680
Go in.

19:18.920 --> 19:20.880
Please go, okay?

19:24.120 --> 19:25.320
Go on.

19:27.400 --> 19:28.520
It will be fine.

19:28.600 --> 19:29.640
You should head back first.

19:41.960 --> 19:43.040
Can I--

19:43.120 --> 19:43.960
Go.

19:47.960 --> 19:50.480
Are you guys hungry by any chance?

19:50.560 --> 19:51.560
Bye. Good night.

20:43.520 --> 20:45.120
Of all the girls, why my sister?

20:46.960 --> 20:48.200
I'm not fooling around.

20:48.280 --> 20:49.160
I'm serious about her.

21:08.320 --> 21:09.280
Come at me.

21:31.320 --> 21:32.600
Come on. Don't stop.

22:01.880 --> 22:03.160
How long has it been going on?

22:06.760 --> 22:07.920
Two and a half months.

22:14.400 --> 22:15.840
Do you even have a conscience?

22:17.920 --> 22:20.120
If you want to date a girl her age

22:20.200 --> 22:22.240
or even younger than her,

22:23.240 --> 22:24.960
I wouldn't object to it.

22:26.520 --> 22:28.480
But this is my sister.

22:29.840 --> 22:32.080
She met you in middle school
and took you as a brother.

22:32.160 --> 22:33.760
How could you target her?

22:41.120 --> 22:42.080
Last time,

22:43.200 --> 22:44.560
I said I would visit you in Nanwu.

22:44.640 --> 22:45.880
It was for this.

22:46.720 --> 22:48.440
I did handle this improperly.

22:52.880 --> 22:53.720
Sorry, buddy.

22:53.800 --> 22:54.880
Who's your buddy?

23:07.120 --> 23:08.400
I know you're upset.

23:09.840 --> 23:10.760
How about this?

23:11.760 --> 23:13.320
You can beat me up however you like.

23:15.040 --> 23:16.200
Idiot.

23:17.200 --> 23:18.160
Okay, my brother?

23:18.240 --> 23:19.240
Don't call me that.

23:31.320 --> 23:32.200
My goodness.

23:45.080 --> 23:46.440
Forget it.

23:46.520 --> 23:48.480
Go home and clean yourself up first.

23:57.800 --> 23:58.880
Thank you, my brother!

24:46.440 --> 24:48.600
SANG ZHI

25:07.680 --> 25:08.960
Aren't you answering, buddy?

25:20.240 --> 25:21.080
SANG ZHI

25:21.160 --> 25:22.720
Is everything okay between you two?

25:33.320 --> 25:35.760
DUAN JIAXU

25:37.480 --> 25:38.760
Everything is fine.

25:38.840 --> 25:39.680
Don't worry.

25:43.480 --> 25:44.440
SANG ZHI

25:44.520 --> 25:46.160
Call me when you can.

25:50.440 --> 25:51.320
Buddy.

25:52.560 --> 25:54.240
I've given serious thought to this matter.

25:54.720 --> 25:55.920
I will be good

25:56.760 --> 25:58.280
to my Zhizhi for the rest of my life.

25:58.920 --> 26:00.280
You don't need to worry about that.

26:01.480 --> 26:02.360
"My Zhizhi"?

26:03.920 --> 26:04.920
Your Zhizhi?

26:08.840 --> 26:09.720
Fine.

26:10.680 --> 26:11.920
She's still yours for now.

26:15.920 --> 26:17.120
Let me ask you something.

26:17.720 --> 26:19.720
Are you sure that you're serious about it?

26:20.840 --> 26:22.920
If not, I would be a total jerk.

26:30.120 --> 26:31.240
Let me ask you this.

26:32.760 --> 26:34.160
How far have you two taken it?

26:35.280 --> 26:36.560
Don't tell me you've already…

26:41.240 --> 26:42.080
Buddy.

26:43.320 --> 26:45.520
Do you see me as someone like that?

26:46.760 --> 26:48.160
Do you wish to hear the truth?

26:50.520 --> 26:52.160
You are someone like that in my eyes.

26:58.960 --> 27:01.440
Besides, you're already 26.

27:01.520 --> 27:03.880
You went after a college freshman.

27:03.960 --> 27:05.240
Are there no limits

27:05.320 --> 27:06.680
to your shamelessness?

27:06.760 --> 27:08.240
Buddy, I'm serious about her.

27:08.320 --> 27:10.080
I'm serious about pursuing her.

27:10.160 --> 27:11.320
Moreover,

27:13.400 --> 27:14.760
we're only five years apart.

27:22.560 --> 27:23.960
If you're not satisfied yet,

27:25.160 --> 27:26.520
why don't you punch me more?

27:29.200 --> 27:30.760
I'm serious. Come at me.

27:33.640 --> 27:35.680
I…

27:35.760 --> 27:37.240
Wait. We're in a cab.

27:40.600 --> 27:41.960
You're really asking for a beating.

27:42.040 --> 27:43.200
I'm speechless.

27:43.840 --> 27:45.360
We can talk about it when we get off.

28:14.440 --> 28:15.480
You can wear my slippers.

28:26.920 --> 28:28.480
Change into my slippers.

28:28.560 --> 28:29.640
You can mop the floor.

28:45.280 --> 28:46.360
Chicken breast.

28:47.200 --> 28:48.080
Strawberries it is.

28:53.840 --> 28:54.720
What?

28:54.800 --> 28:55.840
It's like this.

28:56.400 --> 28:58.000
I hope you won't touch anything

28:58.080 --> 28:59.560
in the refrigerator.

29:00.840 --> 29:01.680
You're so petty.

29:03.840 --> 29:05.560
I bought them for my girlfriend.

29:07.560 --> 29:09.280
"Girlfriend".

29:11.200 --> 29:12.680
I'll just take a bottle of iced tea.

29:12.760 --> 29:14.240
Is there gold in there?

29:17.520 --> 29:19.080
Take a seat. I'm going to shower.

29:23.200 --> 29:24.920
When did you take that photo?

30:18.520 --> 30:19.960
DUAN JIAXU

30:20.040 --> 30:20.960
Are you asleep?

30:21.040 --> 30:22.360
VIDEO CALL

30:23.240 --> 30:24.400
DIALING

30:39.480 --> 30:40.600
VIDEO CALL DECLINED

30:45.640 --> 30:46.840
WHY DID YOU…

30:47.960 --> 30:49.080
I'm not wearing any clothes.

30:54.440 --> 30:55.400
VOICE CALL

31:03.240 --> 31:04.200
Hello?

31:05.040 --> 31:05.920
Hello.

31:07.120 --> 31:09.440
You'll catch a cold
if you don't wear clothes.

31:09.520 --> 31:11.160
Hurry and put on some clothes.

31:12.920 --> 31:14.640
I'm going to sleep soon.

31:14.720 --> 31:15.720
I can't be bothered.

31:18.440 --> 31:20.120
Did something happen

31:21.560 --> 31:22.640
between you and Sang Yan?

31:22.720 --> 31:23.960
No.

31:24.760 --> 31:26.440
He just told me off.

31:29.800 --> 31:30.640
That's good.

31:30.720 --> 31:32.040
Wait, it's not good.

31:33.000 --> 31:34.520
Just let him tell you off first.

31:35.400 --> 31:37.720
I'll find a chance to tell him off later.

31:39.840 --> 31:41.040
Okay, I'll be waiting.

31:43.840 --> 31:46.320
By the way, did he tell you

31:46.400 --> 31:47.960
why he came here?

31:49.400 --> 31:50.560
Your brother

31:50.640 --> 31:52.240
is just concerned about you.

31:52.800 --> 31:55.360
I think he's here to see
if you're cohabiting

31:56.160 --> 31:57.880
with your postgraduate boyfriend.

31:59.800 --> 32:01.320
He's so annoying.

32:01.400 --> 32:02.640
I'm not that easy.

32:06.320 --> 32:09.280
Did he say how long he is staying?

32:10.920 --> 32:13.000
He will probably stay for some time.

32:14.240 --> 32:15.640
All right, don't worry.

32:16.240 --> 32:18.080
I've already explained it to him.

32:19.840 --> 32:21.640
Don't you have work tomorrow?

32:21.720 --> 32:22.600
Sleep early.

32:24.040 --> 32:25.480
You should sleep early too.

32:27.080 --> 32:28.120
Good night.

32:29.840 --> 32:31.000
Good night.

32:32.640 --> 32:33.480
You can hang up.

33:21.160 --> 33:22.080
Xiaoyu.

33:23.640 --> 33:25.200
I've already emailed you

33:25.280 --> 33:26.280
the modified proposal.

33:26.840 --> 33:29.080
That's right. Please take a look.

33:33.640 --> 33:34.520
Bye.

33:36.680 --> 33:38.400
I got a cold. I don't want to infect you.

33:39.240 --> 33:40.480
Let's go.

33:40.560 --> 33:42.240
Why do you suddenly have a cold--

33:48.240 --> 33:49.640
I bumped into something last night.

33:54.120 --> 33:55.240
Bumped into what?

33:55.320 --> 33:56.560
I bumped into

33:57.120 --> 33:59.360
the corner of the nightstand.

34:00.040 --> 34:02.080
- Let's go.
- Are you hurt anywhere else?

34:02.560 --> 34:04.360
No. Only here.

34:07.680 --> 34:08.600
What about him?

34:09.760 --> 34:10.639
Who?

34:11.600 --> 34:12.480
Sang Yan.

34:22.520 --> 34:23.360
Calm down.

34:25.840 --> 34:26.719
That's all.

34:26.800 --> 34:28.159
- Okay, sir. Please wait.
- Sang Zhi.

34:29.639 --> 34:30.520
- Come out.
- What?

34:30.600 --> 34:31.800
- Come!
- What are you doing?

34:31.880 --> 34:34.040
- Come out!
- What are you doing? This is a restaurant.

34:34.120 --> 34:35.080
What are you doing?

34:36.719 --> 34:37.600
Why did you hit him?

34:38.159 --> 34:39.719
Why can't I hit him?

34:39.800 --> 34:42.159
I would've called the cops
if I were there.

34:42.239 --> 34:44.000
I would've told the cops to arrest you!

34:44.080 --> 34:46.239
Go ahead. Call the cops on me if you dare!

34:59.000 --> 35:00.000
I'm cutting ties with you.

35:01.320 --> 35:02.240
You're done for.

35:02.920 --> 35:04.160
From now on,

35:04.240 --> 35:05.840
you're no longer my brother!

35:06.720 --> 35:07.920
Wait.

35:09.800 --> 35:10.680
Sang Zhi.

35:38.080 --> 35:39.040
Is she okay?

35:39.120 --> 35:40.280
She's fine.

35:40.360 --> 35:41.400
She went to the restroom.

35:44.800 --> 35:46.920
Have you been spoiling her rotten?

35:47.800 --> 35:49.640
Her temper has gotten even worse.

35:50.720 --> 35:52.560
Listen. Don't try to stop me later.

35:52.640 --> 35:54.040
I have to teach her a lesson today.

35:54.120 --> 35:55.040
I have to stop you.

35:55.120 --> 35:57.160
Why are you squabbling with a young girl?

35:57.920 --> 35:58.800
Cut it out.

36:03.720 --> 36:06.280
Buddy, tell me when you're free.

36:06.360 --> 36:07.640
Why?

36:07.720 --> 36:09.040
So you can beat me up again.

36:18.320 --> 36:19.240
To be honest,

36:21.680 --> 36:22.640
having my girlfriend

36:23.520 --> 36:25.040
defend me just now

36:28.360 --> 36:29.520
was pretty touching.

37:02.960 --> 37:03.880
Sit.

37:18.280 --> 37:19.480
Do you know how old you are?

37:19.560 --> 37:21.280
Who says "cutting ties" anymore?

37:24.920 --> 37:26.960
Then I'm severing ties,
effective immediately.

37:27.600 --> 37:29.640
Sure. Sever it if you can.

37:32.360 --> 37:33.880
Excuse me.

37:33.960 --> 37:35.120
Sorry for the interruption.

37:36.200 --> 37:38.600
I'm starving. Can we order first?

37:38.680 --> 37:40.040
I already ordered.

37:43.400 --> 37:45.080
You only started dating not long ago,

37:45.160 --> 37:47.120
yet you're already siding

37:47.200 --> 37:48.400
with an outsider.

37:55.920 --> 37:57.000
Sang Yan.

37:57.080 --> 37:57.960
Sang Zhi.

38:00.800 --> 38:02.720
Do you know how to communicate reasonably?

38:02.800 --> 38:04.360
You were born with a mouth.

38:04.440 --> 38:05.920
Can't you talk things over?

38:06.000 --> 38:07.320
Must you get physical?

38:08.440 --> 38:09.840
Be reasonable?

38:09.920 --> 38:12.720
I never resolve issues
with such unproductive methods.

38:12.800 --> 38:13.720
I'm not like you,

38:13.800 --> 38:15.440
never understanding the point.

38:15.520 --> 38:17.280
What do you mean by that?

38:17.360 --> 38:19.160
Since when have I not understood?

38:21.680 --> 38:22.600
I…

38:23.680 --> 38:24.760
I can't imagine

38:24.840 --> 38:27.800
how anyone can get along with you.

38:27.880 --> 38:29.640
You're truly irritating.

38:29.720 --> 38:30.680
Miss,

38:30.760 --> 38:32.320
I was fighting with my buddy.

38:32.400 --> 38:34.080
How is that any of your business?

38:38.280 --> 38:39.520
How is it not my business?

38:39.600 --> 38:41.680
Don't you think
you're wrong for hitting him?

38:41.760 --> 38:43.040
Sang Zhi, calm down.

38:43.120 --> 38:44.320
Being violent is okay?

38:44.400 --> 38:45.480
Have some water.

38:45.560 --> 38:46.800
Sang Zhi, here.

38:48.080 --> 38:50.240
Sang Zhi, calm down.

38:50.320 --> 38:51.840
Why are you arguing with your brother?

38:51.920 --> 38:52.960
You know how he is.

38:53.040 --> 38:54.400
I'm not trying to argue with him.

38:54.480 --> 38:55.640
Just listen to him.

38:55.720 --> 38:57.000
He doesn't think he's wrong.

38:58.280 --> 38:59.400
Look at his lips.

39:00.520 --> 39:01.360
I did that to him.

39:03.920 --> 39:05.800
I also hit him.

39:08.160 --> 39:10.200
But he started the fight, right?

39:10.280 --> 39:12.800
So it was self-defense.

39:13.920 --> 39:15.720
That's really not true.

39:15.800 --> 39:17.560
Last night, he stood without moving

39:17.640 --> 39:18.560
and let me hit him.

39:19.200 --> 39:20.920
So we're already even.

39:21.840 --> 39:23.600
Wait, why did you hit him?

39:24.400 --> 39:25.800
Are both of you this childish?

39:25.880 --> 39:26.960
Can't you two talk it out?

39:27.040 --> 39:28.280
Must you two fight?

39:28.800 --> 39:30.160
Why did you fight?

39:30.760 --> 39:32.360
Couldn't you reason with him?

39:33.200 --> 39:35.280
- You two--
- The little demon does have a conscience.

39:35.360 --> 39:36.240
Tell him.

39:36.320 --> 39:37.440
Teach him how to reason.

39:39.240 --> 39:40.160
I'll eat first.

39:40.680 --> 39:41.520
Let's eat.

39:42.280 --> 39:43.320
You must be hungry.

39:46.400 --> 39:47.680
So did you two immature brats

39:47.760 --> 39:48.840
treat your wounds?

39:48.920 --> 39:50.120
- Yes.
- Yes.

39:53.040 --> 39:54.560
I think there's a bruise here.

39:55.320 --> 39:56.480
Does it hurt?

39:56.560 --> 39:57.560
No.

39:57.640 --> 39:58.800
It's much better now.

39:59.480 --> 40:01.360
No, it must hurt.

40:01.840 --> 40:03.440
- Look at it.
- His is worse.

40:05.440 --> 40:06.600
Look at him.

40:07.280 --> 40:09.000
Someone is doting on Duan Jiaxu now.

40:09.080 --> 40:11.880
Younger sisters

40:11.960 --> 40:13.160
are useless indeed.

40:13.240 --> 40:14.760
I would rather get a girlfriend.

40:14.840 --> 40:16.160
At least a girlfriend

40:16.240 --> 40:18.800
would care about me and feel sorry for me.

40:30.560 --> 40:31.600
Do you want some water?

40:33.680 --> 40:34.920
No.

40:42.600 --> 40:43.960
Since you're in Yihe,

40:44.760 --> 40:46.520
is there any place you want to visit?

40:46.600 --> 40:48.640
I'm busy for the next few days.
I have work.

40:49.200 --> 40:50.640
I'm free on the weekend.

40:51.200 --> 40:53.000
I'm here to visit my buddy.

40:53.080 --> 40:54.480
I don't need your company.

40:54.560 --> 40:55.720
I want my buddy's company.

40:56.560 --> 40:57.600
I'll keep you company.

40:58.640 --> 41:00.720
But I'm bringing my girlfriend.

41:01.280 --> 41:02.440
Suit yourself.

41:02.520 --> 41:03.840
I'll bring her with me then.

41:06.920 --> 41:08.120
Try this shrimp.

41:09.120 --> 41:11.400
I want some shrimp too.

41:14.840 --> 41:16.640
- Are you a thief?
- Aren't you?

41:18.840 --> 41:20.160
You're so irritating.

41:23.560 --> 41:24.480
Try this.

41:27.160 --> 41:28.240
Enough already!

41:28.320 --> 41:29.760
Stop peeling it for her.

41:29.840 --> 41:32.320
Who are you guys trying to show off to?

41:32.400 --> 41:34.080
It's not like I'm peeling it for you.

41:37.760 --> 41:39.040
Isn't it tasty?

41:39.840 --> 41:41.440
- Isn't it yummy?
- It's delicious.

41:41.520 --> 41:42.800
Enough already. Stop!

42:09.520 --> 42:10.760
Do you want to take a shower?

42:11.920 --> 42:12.800
Later.

42:17.160 --> 42:18.680
There isn't another pair of slippers!

42:27.280 --> 42:28.320
Nutcase.

42:42.920 --> 42:45.560
Did you find out about my appendicitis
some time ago?

42:46.240 --> 42:47.080
Yes.

42:47.720 --> 42:49.000
Did you kick me there on purpose?

42:51.640 --> 42:52.880
That kick will fix you.

42:53.800 --> 42:54.720
Look at you.

42:55.360 --> 42:56.960
You should've watched where you hit me.

42:57.760 --> 43:00.080
How am I going to explain my bruise
to her tomorrow?

43:03.240 --> 43:04.520
Applying ointment now is useless.

43:04.600 --> 43:06.160
She will still see it tomorrow.

43:06.720 --> 43:07.560
You're so delicate.

43:11.760 --> 43:12.680
You do have a point.

43:13.960 --> 43:15.920
If the little demon sees you
like this tomorrow,

43:16.000 --> 43:17.400
she'll say that I bullied you.

43:21.400 --> 43:22.280
What about this?

43:22.800 --> 43:23.760
You know me.

43:23.840 --> 43:24.680
I'm a fair person.

43:25.640 --> 43:26.640
Come on. Punch me.

43:32.480 --> 43:33.960
I've never punched someone before.

43:34.040 --> 43:34.920
I don't know how.

43:36.760 --> 43:37.880
Just punch me already.

43:37.960 --> 43:38.880
Stop hesitating.

43:43.520 --> 43:44.520
I have no idea how to.

43:46.440 --> 43:47.480
Stand up.

43:50.520 --> 43:51.520
Make it quick.

43:55.200 --> 43:56.160
Are you okay?

43:59.000 --> 44:01.000
I told you I don't know how to fight.

44:02.320 --> 44:04.040
Here, put some ointment on it.

44:05.280 --> 44:07.080
I'm not as fragile as you.

44:07.960 --> 44:09.320
Put on some ointment.

44:09.400 --> 44:10.320
No, thank you.

44:11.760 --> 44:13.360
Do you need me to apply it for you?

44:15.320 --> 44:16.200
Hurry up.

44:29.360 --> 44:30.640
That's just like you.

44:31.760 --> 44:32.600
Come.

44:40.240 --> 44:42.160
You're a man. Don't be so fragile.

44:47.560 --> 44:48.680
Fine.

44:48.760 --> 44:49.720
Come here.

44:54.480 --> 44:55.400
Do it yourself.

45:19.920 --> 45:21.840
Here's a towel, some clothes,
and a toothbrush.

45:23.640 --> 45:24.800
I have work tomorrow.

45:24.880 --> 45:25.920
I'm going to sleep.

45:26.000 --> 45:27.200
Tell me if you need anything.

45:28.560 --> 45:29.920
Wait. Where do I sleep?

45:34.440 --> 45:36.080
Do you make your guests sleep on the sofa?

45:41.800 --> 45:42.680
Duan Jiaxu!

45:42.760 --> 45:44.040
Duan Jiaxu!

45:44.800 --> 45:45.640
Hey!

45:45.720 --> 45:46.640
What?

45:47.280 --> 45:49.080
You should be the one
sleeping on the sofa!
